title: Episode 376: Triple M (Feat. Malcolm Mays)
itunes:title: Episode 376: Triple M (Feat. Malcolm Mays)
description:
Actor/musician, Malcolm Mays joins the ladies of Lip Service to promote Raising Kanan as well as his latest EP 'Red Flags.' Malcolm opens up about losing his virginity to an older woman, his disappointment in only having sex with white girls on Raising Kanan, and much more. Malcolm even shows the ladies some of his homemade videos...enjoy!
